            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> Iunio <lb n="2"/>Caeciliano <lb n="3"/>Caecilia <lb n="4"/>Regina <lb n="5"/>mater <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>piissimo <lb n="7"/>ex <expan><abbr>decret</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>ord</abbr><ex>inis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuit</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Genio <lb n="2"/>coloniae Ulpiae Traianae <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> Fidelis <lb n="3"/>Septimiae Saloninae Lepcis Magnae <lb n="4"/>Lepcitani devoti
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>IRT 644 was later laid on its rear and IRT 284 was carved on its right side. Interpunktion: IRT 644: hedera. Buchstabenhöhe: IRT 644: 5; IRT 284: 6.</p>
            </div>
